{"tid":2165882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英涉恐嚇記者案今開審　事主常拍攝被告曾遭辱罵","createTime":"2020-08-20T05:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:53:20.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2b11d0c7a36a5e3e47770d363782836ed60016","tid":2165882,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:49:38.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英涉嫌3年前在維園恐嚇一名記者，他早前否認指控，案件原本昨日開審，因天氣關係延至今早在西九龍裁判法院開庭。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，事主X為某報館記者，案發日即2017年6月4日到維園採訪，目睹黎智英與其他人坐在地上，他在遠處將鏡頭對準黎智英，其後X見集會完結就將拍攝工具放下，但被黎智英上前指罵。事主受驚報警，其後轉任其他職位，亦確診適應障礙症併發憂鬱情緒。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544854-20200820.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544854-20200820.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ace790be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544854-20200820.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aa217ba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544854-20200820.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"046636a4ee8b3cbf5097f3594b2fea4db98e9010","tid":2165882,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:53:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WEiT2A1wxPw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWEiT2A1wxPw&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=de8dfe94\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WEiT2A1wxPw</a>"}]}